1. Implement message retention policy in MessageDao:
Future<void> archiveOldMessages() async {
  final cutoff = DateTime.now().subtract(Duration(days: 90));

  // Move to archive table
  await into(messagesArchive).insertAllOnConflictUpdate(
    await (select(messages)..where((m) => m.timestamp.isSmallerThan(cutoff))).get()
  );

  // Delete from main table
  await (delete(messages)..where((m) => m.timestamp.isSmallerThan(cutoff))).go();
}
